subject: Women's British Open (Golf)
Golf
lead_paragraph: Meena Lee of South Korea overcame wet conditions and shot a seven-under 65 Thursday for a two-stroke clubhouse lead in the first round of the Women’s British Open in Carnoustie, Scotland.
